reviewText:
Cyberunk ala Shadowrun, tbh. you could think this game came straight from the Shadowrun IP...which is a good thing.

Dex offeres an interesting Cyberpunkish plot, mixed with the typical Bladerunner and social commentary and lots of quite surprisingly good voice-acting;

you get the typical rpg-mechanics and skills, like hacking" or "lockpicking" and ofcourse combat skills
